dct_title_s: Regional development plan : Atlanta five-county metropolitan planning district
dct_description_sm: Maps showing population distribution; political boundaries; drainage basins; regional rapid transit system; expressway plan; expressway influence area; and vacant land on verso. Explanatory notes, maps and bibliography on verso.
dct_publisher_sm: Atlanta : Atlanta Region Metropolitan Planning Commission, 1962.
